{
  "name": "ColorFormat",
  "summary": "<p>可以将颜色设为显式的红-绿-蓝值（使用 <strong>RGB</strong> 属性），或设为配色方案中的一种颜色（使用 <strong>SchemeColor</strong> 属性）。</p>\n<p>使用下表中列出的属性之一可返回 <strong>ColorFormat</strong>对象。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>使用此属性</th>\n<th>对象</th>\n<th>返回一个 ColorFormat 对象，该对象代表</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>BackColor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>FillFormat</strong></td>\n<td>背景填充色（用于阴影或图案填充格式）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>ForeColor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>FillFormat</strong></td>\n<td>前景填充色（对于纯色填充格式，即代表填充颜色）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>BackColor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>LineFormat</strong></td>\n<td>线条背景色（用于图案线条）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>ForeColor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>LineFormat</strong></td>\n<td>线条前景色（对于纯色线条，即代表线条颜色）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>ForeColor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>ShadowFormat</strong></td>\n<td>阴影颜色</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>ExtrusionColor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>ThreeDFormat</strong></td>\n<td>有延伸的对象的侧边颜色</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>RGB</strong> 属性可将颜色设置为显示的红-绿-蓝值。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例向第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，然后设置矩形填充的前景色、背景色和渐变。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> fillFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>\n    fillFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">128</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    fillFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">170</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">170</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">170</span>)\n    fillFormat.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TwoColorGradient</span>(msoGradientHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一个形状阴影的前景色的颜色类型是否为 msoColorTypeRGB。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Shapes</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoColorTypeRGB)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表单色对象的颜色、带有渐变或图案填充的对象的前景或背景色，或者指针的颜色。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Brightness",
      "summary": "<p>该属性的值必须是 0.0（最暗）到 1.0（最亮）之间的数字。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象的发光度。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表中第一个形状的前景填充色的亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第二个形状背景填充色的亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ObjectThemeColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一种映射到主题配色方案的颜色。可读/写 <strong>MsoThemeColorIndex</strong>。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第二个形状背景填充色映射到主题配色方案的颜色是否为无主题颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ObjectThemeColor</span> == msoNotThemeColor)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表中第一个形状前景填充色映射到主题配色方案的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ObjectThemeColor</span> = msoThemeColorDark2\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoThemeColorIndex",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "RGB",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表指定颜色的红绿蓝 (RGB) 值。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第二个形状背景填充色是否为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表中第一个形状前景填充色为绿色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SchemeColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Integer</strong> 值，它代表 <strong>Color</strong> 对象的颜色，作为当前配色方案中的索引。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表中第一个形状前景填充色的当前配色方案。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SchemeColor</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第二个形状背景填充色的当前配色方案是否为绿色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SchemeColor</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "TintAndShade",
      "summary": "<p>可以为 <strong>TintAndShade</strong> 属性输入 -1（最暗）到 1（最亮）之间的数字，零 (0) 为中间值。  </p>\n<p>如果将此属性设置为小于 -1 或大于 1 的值，则会引起运行时错误：“指定的值超出了范围”。此属性用于主题颜色和非主题颜色。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Single</strong>，使颜色变深或变浅。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第一个形状前景填充色的TintAndShade属性值设置为-1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第二个形状背景填充色的TintAndShade属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个代表颜色格式类型的 <strong>MsoColorType</strong> 值。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断活动工作表中第一个形状前景填充色的颜色类型，并显示结果。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoColorTypeScheme) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;颜色由应用程序特定的方案定义。&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;其他类型&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上第二个形状背景填充色的颜色类型是否为 msoColorTypeRGB。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BackColor</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(colorFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoColorTypeRGB)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoColorType",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}